%% ActivaClub - Stripe Payment + Webhook Flow (EP-04)
%% Diagram 7 of 8
%% Last updated: 2026-04-05

sequenceDiagram
    participant Member
    participant Frontend
    participant PaymentsLambda
    participant DynamoDB as DynamoDB (PaymentsTable + MembersTable)
    participant Stripe

    Member->>Frontend: Click "Pagar Membresía"
    Frontend->>PaymentsLambda: POST /v1/payments/checkout { billingCycle }
    PaymentsLambda->>Stripe: Create Checkout Session
    Stripe-->>PaymentsLambda: { sessionId, sessionUrl }
    PaymentsLambda->>DynamoDB: PutItem payment (status=Pending)
    PaymentsLambda-->>Frontend: { sessionUrl }
    Frontend->>Stripe: Redirect to Stripe Checkout
    Member->>Stripe: Complete payment
    Stripe->>PaymentsLambda: POST /v1/payments/webhook (checkout.session.completed)
    PaymentsLambda->>PaymentsLambda: Verify Stripe signature
    PaymentsLambda->>DynamoDB: UpdateItem payment (status=Succeeded)
    PaymentsLambda->>DynamoDB: UpdateItem member (status=Active, membershipExpiry=+1 month/year)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Redirect to success page
